# api Directory Guide

The [api/](mdc:api) directory contains the backend API server logic, including:

- [ragflow_server.py](mdc:api/ragflow_server.py): Main API server implementation.
- [settings.py](mdc:api/settings.py): API configuration settings.
- [versions.py](mdc:api/versions.py): API versioning information.
- [validation.py](mdc:api/validation.py): Input validation logic.
- [constants.py](mdc:api/constants.py): API constants.
- [utils/](mdc:api/utils): Utility functions for the API.
- [db/](mdc:api/db): Database-related logic and models.
- [apps/](mdc:api/apps): Application-specific API endpoints.

See each referenced file or subdirectory for more details on the API backend.
